                                        <due></due>
                            <votes>0</votes>
                                    <watches>1</watches>
                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12833995" author="jdcryans" created="Mon, 15 Feb 2010 21:40:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m changing the title to include a wider scope of features, working on this I found that we could use such a MR to copy a table on the same cluster (using a different name).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12834374" author="jdcryans" created="Tue, 16 Feb 2010 18:46:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch that adds a new MR job called CopyTable that can be configured with a peer cluster address, new table name, time range and a different region server implementation (if the peer is different). It also modifies TOF to accept the peer address and the configuration of a different region server implementation. A test is added to TestReplication to use CopyTable (which will be modified once &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1728&quot; title=&quot;Column family scoping and cluster identification&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-1728&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-1728&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; gets in to care about scoping).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12835074" author="jdcryans" created="Thu, 18 Feb 2010 00:28:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Version 2 of the patch cares about &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1728&quot; title=&quot;Column family scoping and cluster identification&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-1728&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-1728&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and does some more cleanup in TestReplication.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12835426" author="ryanobjc" created="Thu, 18 Feb 2010 21:51:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12835445" author="jdcryans" created="Thu, 18 Feb 2010 22:28:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed to trunk, thanks for the review Ryan!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12835619" author="kaykay.unique" created="Fri, 19 Feb 2010 07:05:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Would there be a mapred version of this ? &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15017868" author="lars_francke" created="Fri, 20 Nov 2015 13:01:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This issue was closed as part of a bulk closing operation on 2015-11-20. All issues that have been resolved and where all fixVersions have been released have been closed (following discussions on the mailing list).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
